{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Financial Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff0000; /* Pure Red */\n            --secondary-color: #330000; /* Dark Red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a0000; /* Very Dark Red */\n            --accent-color: #ff6666; /* Lighter Red */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            padding: 2rem 4rem;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 100;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,') no-repeat center center;\n            background-size: cover;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26, 0, 0, 0.8) 0%, rgba(51, 0, 0, 0.8) 100%);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .services {\n            padding: 6rem 4rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .services::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(51, 0, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .services h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n\n        .contact {\n            padding: 6rem 4rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .contact::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n                45deg,\n                rgba(51, 0, 0, 0.05),\n                rgba(51, 0, 0, 0.05) 10px,\n                rgba(26, 0, 0, 0.1) 10px,\n                rgba(26, 0, 0, 0.1) 20px\n            );\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 1rem;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                padding: 1.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .logo {\n                margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            }\n\n            nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 0.5rem 0;\n            }\n\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3rem;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n            }\n\n            .services, .contact {\n                padding: 3rem 1.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .services h2, .contact h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .service-item {\n                padding: 1.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .service-item h3 {\n                font-size: 1.5rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"logo\">Quantum Financial</div>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1>Navigate the Future of Finance</h1>\n            <p>\n                Precision strategies and innovative solutions for your financial growth.\n                We blend cutting-edge technology with expert insights to secure your future.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services\">\n        <h2>Our Advanced Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Strategic Investment</h3>\n                <p>\n                    Leveraging predictive analytics and AI to identify high-yield opportunities\n                    and mitigate risks in dynamic markets.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                <p>\n                    Implementing robust frameworks and real-time monitoring to safeguard\n                    your assets against unforeseen market fluctuations.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Wealth Preservation</h3>\n                <p>\n                    Tailored plans designed to protect and grow your wealth, ensuring\n                    long-term security and legacy building.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Algorithmic Trading</h3>\n                <p>\n                    Developing and deploying sophisticated algorithms for automated,\n                    efficient trading execution with unparalleled precision.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Connect with Our Experts</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\">\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\">\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\"></textarea>\n            <button>Send Inquiry</button>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2024 Quantum Financial Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}